{"id": "6125", "post": "<div class=\"post-6125 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-christmas2014\" id=\"post-6125\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/merry-christmas-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Merry Christmas</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/christmas2014/\" rel=\"tag\">christmas2014</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> December 24, 2014 @ 2:00 pm, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner.png\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4755 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner.png.webp\" alt=\"Christmas Banner\" width=\"900\" height=\"255\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner.png.webp 900w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner-300x85.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner.png.webp 900w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Christmas-Banner-300x85.png.webp 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><p>Dear LowEndBox reader,</p><p>Thank you for having been part of the LowEndBox and LowEndTalk communities for yet another year, or any part thereof. It is you, the people, that enable me and my team to run these magnificent websites!</p><p>I hope that all your Christmases will be good and prosperous and that you may celebrate Christmas with your loved ones. Because as much fun as servers and these websites may be, we should not forget about the real world and those around us: the people that help and enable us to do these great things.</p><p>On behalf of Jon, Alex, and their colleagues at ColoCrossing, Asim, Mikael, and Rashid at LowEndBox, and Spirit, jcaleb, vedran, and Nekki at LowEndTalk I would like to wish you and your loved ones a very Merry Christmas!</p><p>Maarten</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmerry-christmas-2%2F&amp;t=Merry%20Christmas\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Merry%20Christmas&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmerry-christmas-2%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmerry-christmas-2%2F&amp;title=Merry%20Christmas&amp;mini=true\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-linkedin dpsp-no-label dpsp-last\" title=\"Share on LinkedIn\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span c